        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued May 27 at 2:40PM MDT by NWS Denver CO</headline>
        <description>At 240 PM MDT, Doppler radar was tracking a strong thunderstorm 7
miles southeast of Willadsen Estates, or 17 miles southwest of
Cheyenne, moving southeast at 20 mph.

HAZARD...Half inch size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Minor damage to outdoor objects is possible.

Locations impacted include...
Natural Fort, Carr and Rockport.
</description>
        <instruction>Monitor the weather situation closely and be alert for threatening
weather conditions.</instruction>
